:: Rainchark dodges the missle easily by swerving to his left.  
Rainchark fires 2 missles at Holocaust, and flies away at a high 
speed, trying to get away from Holocaust and Pyrotaur.  He couldn't 
win when he was double-teamed, so he hoped he could shake one of them 
off.  Then deliver the final blow. ::
